1
00:00:17,940 --> 00:00:21,260
♪The falling snow♪

2
00:00:21,620 --> 00:00:25,180
♪Is bitter cold♪

3
00:00:27,300 --> 00:00:29,980
♪My sigh♪

4
00:00:30,420 --> 00:00:34,460
♪Misted the path in front of me♪

5
00:00:36,620 --> 00:00:42,740
♪The moonlight knows my intention♪

6
00:00:44,860 --> 00:00:51,300
♪I just want to make a place for me
in your heart♪

7
00:00:53,820 --> 00:00:57,620
♪I laugh and I cry♪

8
00:00:58,340 --> 00:01:02,100
♪Quietly building a pond in my heart♪

9
00:01:02,900 --> 00:01:06,780
♪I accept all the gifts from sorrow♪

10
00:01:07,580 --> 00:01:11,420
♪I can't let down my regrets♪

11
00:01:12,060 --> 00:01:15,860
♪I won't admit defeat♪

12
00:01:16,460 --> 00:01:20,260
♪I slowly chew on
the bitterness of life♪

13
00:01:20,980 --> 00:01:24,540
♪The fragrance remains the same
after the bleak winter♪

14
00:01:25,340 --> 00:01:29,540
♪Awaiting spring
to color the way back home♪

15
00:01:31,020 --> 00:01:36,340
[The Double]

16
00:01:36,340 --> 00:01:39,020
[Episode 20]

17
00:01:39,560 --> 00:01:40,280
Gold mine?

18
00:01:41,950 --> 00:01:42,590
Hurry up!

19
00:01:44,920 --> 00:01:46,200
Xue's family of three,

20
00:01:49,200 --> 00:01:50,070
Shen Yurong,

21
00:01:50,640 --> 00:01:51,400
and Eldest Princess...

22
00:01:52,510 --> 00:01:54,120
Everything is connected.

23
00:01:54,590 --> 00:01:55,400
So

24
00:01:56,680 --> 00:01:58,000
do you know

25
00:01:58,000 --> 00:01:59,480
what's in it for you?

26
00:02:00,200 --> 00:02:01,480
What's in it?

27
00:02:04,760 --> 00:02:06,840
Didn't they kill everyone?

28
00:02:06,840 --> 00:02:07,310
You're right.

29
00:02:10,630 --> 00:02:12,630
Move around to avoid suspicion.

30
00:02:16,000 --> 00:02:16,710
Be quick.

31
00:02:19,030 --> 00:02:19,590
Hurry up.

32
00:02:20,120 --> 00:02:21,120
You're so darn poky.

33
00:02:21,310 --> 00:02:22,150
Didn't you have breakfast?

34
00:02:24,190 --> 00:02:24,800
Hurry up.

35
00:02:31,520 --> 00:02:32,520
Come on, you two!

36
00:02:34,360 --> 00:02:35,430
- Er.
- Hurry up! What are you doing?

37
00:02:35,680 --> 00:02:37,470
What are you doing? It's an easy task.

38
00:02:37,800 --> 00:02:38,240
I'll kill you.

39
00:02:38,240 --> 00:02:39,240
Stop it.

40
00:02:39,310 --> 00:02:39,840
Get out of the way.

41
00:02:39,910 --> 00:02:40,470
Stop it.

42
00:02:40,560 --> 00:02:41,800
I'll kill you too.

43
00:02:42,030 --> 00:02:42,400
Official.

44
00:02:42,400 --> 00:02:43,030
I'll kill you too.

45
00:02:43,030 --> 00:02:44,000
- Stop.
- I'll kill you.

46
00:02:44,000 --> 00:02:45,150
Don't hit my brother!

47
00:02:45,520 --> 00:02:46,240
Go away!

48
00:02:46,680 --> 00:02:47,590
You will join him in death.

49
00:02:47,590 --> 00:02:48,190
Official.

50
00:02:48,910 --> 00:02:50,240
- Er.
- Stop.

51
00:02:50,240 --> 00:02:51,030
I'll kill you.

52
00:02:51,150 --> 00:02:52,190
- Stop it.
- I'll kill you.

53
00:02:52,680 --> 00:02:54,000
There are fewer workers now than before.

54
00:02:54,150 --> 00:02:55,680
Who will do the work if we kill them?
Calm down.

55
00:02:56,560 --> 00:02:57,710
I'll let you off.

56
00:02:57,960 --> 00:02:59,630
Go back and nurse your injuries.
Then come back to work.

57
00:02:59,630 --> 00:03:00,470
- Go!
- Let's go.

58
00:03:00,470 --> 00:03:01,680
You'll have nothing to eat
if you come back late!

59
00:03:01,910 --> 00:03:03,630
What are you looking at?

60
00:03:04,030 --> 00:03:04,470
Let's go.

61
00:03:06,280 --> 00:03:07,680
You see.

62
00:03:08,470 --> 00:03:09,870
If you dare to shirk,

63
00:03:10,000 --> 00:03:11,120
you will be like them.

64
00:03:11,560 --> 00:03:12,240
Stop looking! Get to work.

65
00:03:12,240 --> 00:03:13,630
Hurry up. What are you doing? Hurry up.

66
00:03:32,000 --> 00:03:32,710
Hang in there.

67
00:03:36,560 --> 00:03:38,800
Are we going to die here?

68
00:03:40,800 --> 00:03:43,520
Don't talk nonsense. We'll be fine.

69
00:03:59,710 --> 00:04:00,280
Who is it?

70
00:04:08,800 --> 00:04:09,630
The foreman said

71
00:04:10,190 --> 00:04:11,470
we can go back after dressing the wound.

72
00:04:14,560 --> 00:04:16,070
Stay over there. Don't force us.

73
00:04:28,830 --> 00:04:29,510
Gu Da.

74
00:04:29,830 --> 00:04:30,510
Gu Er.

75
00:04:31,680 --> 00:04:32,390
It's me.

76
00:04:33,950 --> 00:04:35,190
Xue Li?

77
00:04:38,040 --> 00:04:38,830
It's Xue Li.

78
00:04:40,870 --> 00:04:41,480
It's me.

79
00:04:42,240 --> 00:04:43,310
You are Xue Li?

80
00:04:44,950 --> 00:04:46,070
I'm here to save you.

81
00:04:48,600 --> 00:04:49,560
I'm sorry to get you into trouble.

82
00:04:49,680 --> 00:04:50,160
But...

83
00:04:50,430 --> 00:04:51,430
But didn't the rumor say

84
00:04:51,600 --> 00:04:52,920
that you had an accident
on your way back to your hometown?

85
00:04:53,160 --> 00:04:53,720
How could you...

86
00:04:53,950 --> 00:04:55,160
It's a long story.

87
00:04:56,120 --> 00:04:57,600
I have a new identity now.

88
00:04:57,750 --> 00:04:58,600
I'm called Jiang Li.

89
00:04:59,270 --> 00:05:00,040
Jiang Li?

90
00:05:00,720 --> 00:05:01,950
From now on, don't call me

91
00:05:02,630 --> 00:05:04,190
by my old name in front of outsiders.

92
00:05:05,430 --> 00:05:07,310
Let yourselves out,
and I'll tell you in detail.

93
00:05:08,120 --> 00:05:09,040
It's heavily guarded here.

94
00:05:09,950 --> 00:05:11,360
It's not that easy to escape.

95
00:05:11,680 --> 00:05:12,160
He's right.

96
00:05:12,560 --> 00:05:13,480
Xue Li, just go.

97
00:05:13,800 --> 00:05:14,870
Even if we escape,

98
00:05:15,120 --> 00:05:16,040
Feng Yutang

99
00:05:16,040 --> 00:05:17,000
won't let us go.

100
00:05:17,270 --> 00:05:18,310
- Yes, hurry up.
- I'm not leaving.

101
00:05:18,310 --> 00:05:19,310
Go.

102
00:05:19,310 --> 00:05:20,160
I'm not leaving.

103
00:05:21,070 --> 00:05:21,720
Don't worry.

104
00:05:22,560 --> 00:05:25,000
It's time to bring Feng Yutang
down a peg or two.

105
00:05:25,800 --> 00:05:26,720
Now that I've come in,

106
00:05:27,310 --> 00:05:28,720
I must take you out.

107
00:05:31,750 --> 00:05:32,720
Let's go over there and see.

108
00:05:32,950 --> 00:05:33,870
Let's see if anyone is lazy.

109
00:05:34,160 --> 00:05:34,600
All right.

110
00:05:51,480 --> 00:05:52,720
Don't be frightened! He is one of us.

111
00:05:52,720 --> 00:05:53,390
Somebody is coming.

112
00:06:08,360 --> 00:06:09,240
Are you going to knock me to death?

113
00:06:12,380 --> 00:06:13,890
Behave yourself and work hard!

114
00:06:15,260 --> 00:06:16,820
My brother told you

115
00:06:16,820 --> 00:06:17,740
to be more productive.

116
00:06:20,210 --> 00:06:21,330
What's going on with you today?

117
00:06:22,850 --> 00:06:23,770
Work hard.

118
00:06:26,260 --> 00:06:27,740
Wait for me.

119
00:07:14,020 --> 00:07:15,020
Are you skipping dinner?

120
00:07:15,210 --> 00:07:15,890
Do you want to starve me to death?

121
00:07:15,890 --> 00:07:16,970
No.

122
00:07:49,770 --> 00:07:50,330
Where are they?

123
00:07:51,850 --> 00:07:53,180
I watched them come in.

124
00:08:13,890 --> 00:08:14,380
Xue...

125
00:08:15,850 --> 00:08:16,450
Li.

126
00:08:17,450 --> 00:08:18,380
We have thought about it.

127
00:08:18,940 --> 00:08:20,210
You come and save us with courage.

128
00:08:20,410 --> 00:08:21,410
Why don't we dare to go out?

129
00:08:22,330 --> 00:08:23,090
But

130
00:08:23,890 --> 00:08:25,650
He Jun and Peng Xiao are also here.

131
00:08:26,060 --> 00:08:27,650
Are He Jun and Peng Xiao still alive?

132
00:08:27,940 --> 00:08:29,620
Er and I will call on them.

133
00:08:30,060 --> 00:08:31,020
Be careful.

134
00:08:32,100 --> 00:08:32,980
Don't give the game away.

135
00:08:33,500 --> 00:08:34,170
Don't worry.

136
00:08:35,170 --> 00:08:35,930
- Let's go.
- Go.

137
00:08:48,620 --> 00:08:49,620
Keep up.

138
00:08:50,410 --> 00:08:51,020
Hurry up.

139
00:08:53,100 --> 00:08:53,810
This way.

140
00:08:55,810 --> 00:08:56,530
All right, go.

141
00:08:56,530 --> 00:08:57,570
After dinner,

142
00:08:57,650 --> 00:08:58,810
another shift will take over.

143
00:08:58,980 --> 00:08:59,340
Here you go.

144
00:09:00,100 --> 00:09:01,380
Let's take this opportunity

145
00:09:01,460 --> 00:09:02,890
to get Peng Xiao and He Jun.

146
00:09:02,890 --> 00:09:03,740
All right, that's all.

147
00:09:04,380 --> 00:09:04,740
Da.

148
00:09:04,860 --> 00:09:05,290
Go.

149
00:09:05,740 --> 00:09:07,290
He Jun and Peng Xiao are over there.

150
00:09:07,500 --> 00:09:08,050
Hurry up.

151
00:09:09,410 --> 00:09:09,860
Let's go.

152
00:09:13,220 --> 00:09:13,690
Yours.

153
00:09:15,100 --> 00:09:15,980
No time to explain.

154
00:09:16,050 --> 00:09:16,460
Let's go.

155
00:09:18,500 --> 00:09:18,980
Go.

156
00:09:24,340 --> 00:09:25,410
Your shoulders are shaking.

157
00:09:27,220 --> 00:09:28,050
You're mistaken.

158
00:09:29,740 --> 00:09:31,140
As someone who was dragged
into the game by you,

159
00:09:31,460 --> 00:09:32,810
I need to remind you.

160
00:09:33,140 --> 00:09:34,340
This operation is too risky.

161
00:09:34,930 --> 00:09:35,860
With your intelligence,

162
00:09:35,890 --> 00:09:37,100
you can wait until I destroy them

163
00:09:37,100 --> 00:09:39,100
and get a free ride.

164
00:09:39,380 --> 00:09:40,260
Why not?

165
00:09:41,050 --> 00:09:42,340
By the time
you gather sufficient evidence

166
00:09:42,340 --> 00:09:43,810
and send troops to seize the gold mine,

167
00:09:44,650 --> 00:09:46,570
Magistrate Xue has been beheaded.

168
00:09:48,460 --> 00:09:49,100
Come.

169
00:10:08,050 --> 00:10:08,570
Oh, no!

170
00:10:09,770 --> 00:10:11,290
They don't know
that the inspectors are approaching.

171
00:10:11,650 --> 00:10:12,410
We have to go back.

172
00:10:13,740 --> 00:10:14,340
Follow me.

173
00:10:28,650 --> 00:10:29,460
Quick, hide!

174
00:10:29,460 --> 00:10:29,740
Come.

175
00:10:42,170 --> 00:10:42,620
Er.

176
00:10:47,020 --> 00:10:47,620
Be quiet.

177
00:10:47,930 --> 00:10:48,500
Calm down.

178
00:10:49,260 --> 00:10:50,620
If the worst comes to the worst,
we'll fight.

179
00:10:51,050 --> 00:10:51,690
You're right.

180
00:10:52,220 --> 00:10:54,690
There are four of us and two of them.

181
00:11:07,170 --> 00:11:09,410
I feel like sleeping when I'm full.

182
00:11:09,890 --> 00:11:11,260
All you do is eat and sleep.

183
00:11:20,380 --> 00:11:21,860
Help! Something happened.

184
00:11:21,860 --> 00:11:22,810
Help!

185
00:11:23,260 --> 00:11:24,860
Something's up. Help!

186
00:11:24,860 --> 00:11:26,570
Help! Something's up.

187
00:11:36,170 --> 00:11:36,740
Step back.

188
00:11:36,890 --> 00:11:38,410
Over there! Catch them.

189
00:12:27,500 --> 00:12:28,500
My Lord, please go first.

190
00:12:28,740 --> 00:12:29,460
Come back alive.

191
00:12:29,740 --> 00:12:30,140
Yes.

192
00:12:35,860 --> 00:12:36,170
Let's go.

193
00:12:38,290 --> 00:12:38,620
Go.

194
00:13:00,340 --> 00:13:01,650
You can't even guard a person.

195
00:13:03,220 --> 00:13:04,260
You let him run away.

196
00:13:04,460 --> 00:13:06,340
What's the use
of keeping a dead loss like you?

197
00:13:06,770 --> 00:13:07,810
Magistrate, don't worry.

198
00:13:07,930 --> 00:13:09,770
We have been searching
the whole city for Ye Mingyu.

199
00:13:10,530 --> 00:13:11,810
He will not be able
to escape from Huaixiang.

200
00:13:12,460 --> 00:13:13,380
Rest assured.

201
00:13:14,140 --> 00:13:15,020
Rest assured?

202
00:13:15,290 --> 00:13:16,650
Have you ever reassured me?

203
00:13:17,500 --> 00:13:18,260
Magistrate, please calm down.

204
00:13:18,690 --> 00:13:20,220
When we were searching,

205
00:13:20,690 --> 00:13:24,340
we found that there was a spy

206
00:13:25,050 --> 00:13:26,020
in yamen.

207
00:14:06,930 --> 00:14:10,650
Xue Huaiyuan took you in back then.

208
00:14:11,260 --> 00:14:14,860
To return the favor,
you are willing to die.

209
00:14:15,050 --> 00:14:17,020
I didn't expect
that there would be someone

210
00:14:18,260 --> 00:14:20,860
as kind and righteous as you in yamen.

211
00:14:22,690 --> 00:14:23,690
And look at you.

212
00:14:24,930 --> 00:14:26,410
A pack of dogs.

213
00:14:27,140 --> 00:14:28,290
Maybe one day

214
00:14:29,050 --> 00:14:30,890
you will sell me for money.

215
00:14:36,410 --> 00:14:37,460
There's just one thing

216
00:14:38,140 --> 00:14:40,050
I can't figure out.

217
00:14:42,140 --> 00:14:46,860
I took you in
after Xue Huaiyuan fell from power.

218
00:14:47,570 --> 00:14:49,570
I am your benefactor, too.

219
00:14:49,980 --> 00:14:51,570
Why did you betray me?

220
00:14:52,140 --> 00:14:52,770
Crook!

221
00:14:54,100 --> 00:14:56,260
You didn't deserve
to be compared with Magistrate Xue.

222
00:15:04,290 --> 00:15:06,890
I thought you were dumb.

223
00:15:07,410 --> 00:15:09,050
Since you are not dumb,

224
00:15:10,020 --> 00:15:10,980
tell me

225
00:15:13,260 --> 00:15:17,810
if Jiang Li is Xue Fangfei.

226
00:15:18,100 --> 00:15:19,020
Where is she?

227
00:15:19,740 --> 00:15:22,500
What did you say?

228
00:15:27,260 --> 00:15:32,140
If you don't tell me, I'll be angry.

229
00:15:33,220 --> 00:15:33,690
Fine.

230
00:15:35,740 --> 00:15:36,570
I'll tell you.

231
00:15:43,500 --> 00:15:46,570
She told me that day that...

232
00:15:49,020 --> 00:15:51,170
Go to hell, you crook!

233
00:16:06,860 --> 00:16:08,170
Bring Guai here.

234
00:16:09,050 --> 00:16:11,050
It hasn't eaten meat for days.

235
00:16:12,930 --> 00:16:14,620
She is just enough for a good feed.

236
00:16:15,380 --> 00:16:16,690
This hag

237
00:16:17,020 --> 00:16:19,260
has only uttered a few words
in her life.

238
00:16:19,690 --> 00:16:20,650
This time,

239
00:16:21,410 --> 00:16:23,020
let her scream.

240
00:17:10,660 --> 00:17:11,180
My Lord.

241
00:17:11,940 --> 00:17:13,130
Get in the carriage. I'll deal with it.

242
00:17:13,220 --> 00:17:14,370
Lu Ji is still behind us.
Go and pick him up.

243
00:17:14,370 --> 00:17:14,770
All right.

244
00:17:17,260 --> 00:17:17,700
Come.

245
00:17:18,420 --> 00:17:18,850
Get in.

246
00:17:23,770 --> 00:17:24,290
Follow me.

247
00:17:24,530 --> 00:17:24,980
All right.

248
00:17:35,090 --> 00:17:35,770
Report!

249
00:17:38,770 --> 00:17:39,370
Report.

250
00:17:39,700 --> 00:17:41,530
Magistrate,
there's a report from the mine.

251
00:17:41,740 --> 00:17:43,850
The miners were rescued by someone.

252
00:17:45,980 --> 00:17:48,530
So their goal is the gold mine.

253
00:17:54,530 --> 00:17:56,260
Is there any letter from above?

254
00:17:56,900 --> 00:17:57,850
Not yet.

255
00:17:58,850 --> 00:17:59,770
No?

256
00:18:00,260 --> 00:18:01,220
- Magistrate!
- No?

257
00:18:01,460 --> 00:18:02,570
- No?
- Please spare me, Magistrate.

258
00:18:02,570 --> 00:18:03,570
- Always no!
- Please spare me, Magistrate.

259
00:18:03,570 --> 00:18:04,530
- Why none?
- Please spare me, Magistrate.

260
00:18:04,980 --> 00:18:05,500
Get out!

261
00:18:06,610 --> 00:18:08,220
Magistrate, there is a pigeon post

262
00:18:08,740 --> 00:18:09,530
from the capital.

263
00:18:24,420 --> 00:18:27,330
Since I have someone to support me
even if the sky falls,

264
00:18:28,570 --> 00:18:31,460
I don't have anything to worry about.

265
00:18:32,810 --> 00:18:35,370
If you dare to challenge me
on my home ground,

266
00:18:36,500 --> 00:18:39,260
I will make sure
you never come out alive.

267
00:19:09,220 --> 00:19:10,420
There's an ambush.
Get out of the carriage.

268
00:21:15,290 --> 00:21:15,770
Xiao Heng!

269
00:21:38,610 --> 00:21:40,050
Lu Ji, protect Li!

270
00:21:40,130 --> 00:21:40,460
Yes!

271
00:22:30,570 --> 00:22:31,460
Are you all right?

272
00:22:53,570 --> 00:22:55,570
My Lord, the wound has been dressed
with bandages.

273
00:22:55,700 --> 00:22:56,610
Try to move.

274
00:23:04,090 --> 00:23:04,770
Stop.

275
00:23:05,900 --> 00:23:06,740
Lower your head.

276
00:23:25,020 --> 00:23:25,900
Does it hurt?

277
00:23:29,370 --> 00:23:30,130
It's nothing.

278
00:23:30,700 --> 00:23:31,330
What about you?

279
00:23:31,570 --> 00:23:32,810
You protected me.

280
00:23:33,810 --> 00:23:34,700
I'm fine.

281
00:23:36,770 --> 00:23:38,090
I also got it bandaged just now.

282
00:23:39,850 --> 00:23:40,610
Li.

283
00:23:41,460 --> 00:23:42,740
You don't have to be a bravado.

284
00:23:46,740 --> 00:23:47,900
My life is yours now.

285
00:23:50,570 --> 00:23:52,260
Did you hear me?

286
00:23:52,740 --> 00:23:53,500
I did.

287
00:23:53,740 --> 00:23:54,810
But it means little.

