579
00:41:45,870 --> 00:41:46,430
Enough already!

580
00:41:50,950 --> 00:41:53,430
I wanted to redress the injustices
for Magistrate Xue.

581
00:41:55,830 --> 00:41:57,350
I submitted a petition

582
00:41:58,260 --> 00:42:00,030
when I learned
that Magistrate Xue was convicted.

583
00:42:00,870 --> 00:42:02,070
But the new county magistrate

584
00:42:04,620 --> 00:42:06,740
beat the hell out of my mother.

585
00:42:08,870 --> 00:42:10,550
Feng Yutang is dead.

586
00:42:11,390 --> 00:42:12,700
Why are you still afraid of him?

587
00:42:13,030 --> 00:42:14,870
We are just ordinary people.

588
00:42:16,260 --> 00:42:18,260
We only want to live.

589
00:42:18,510 --> 00:42:19,990
I can only repay

590
00:42:20,620 --> 00:42:21,430
Magistrate Xue's kindness

591
00:42:22,700 --> 00:42:24,350
in my next life.

592
00:42:27,180 --> 00:42:29,030
