593
00:42:29,470 --> 00:42:30,740
no one will come forward.

594
00:42:34,870 --> 00:42:37,510
When they confiscated Xue's Residence,

595
00:42:38,350 --> 00:42:38,990
I went there.

596
00:42:39,550 --> 00:42:40,390
How did it end?

597
00:42:41,140 --> 00:42:43,100
I was struck blind in one eye by them.

598
00:42:43,700 --> 00:42:45,620
I don't want to lose another eye.

599
00:42:46,830 --> 00:42:47,660
We went to

600
00:42:48,070 --> 00:42:49,260
several of the villagers' homes.

601
00:42:49,470 --> 00:42:52,140
Zhang, Dai Yun, and Mo Wenxuan.

602
00:42:53,260 --> 00:42:53,990
They...

603
00:42:54,620 --> 00:42:55,390
Got it.

604
00:42:56,910 --> 00:42:58,510
Go back first.

605
00:42:59,830 --> 00:43:00,700
Thank you.

606
00:43:00,950 --> 00:43:03,660
