607
00:43:03,950 --> 00:43:04,350
He's right.

608
00:43:06,100 --> 00:43:07,550
Magistrate Xue is kind-hearted.

609
00:43:08,910 --> 00:43:10,260
God will take care of him.

610
00:43:10,780 --> 00:43:13,990
Sure, one good turn deserves another.

611
00:43:34,780 --> 00:43:35,660
Aunt Chunfang.

612
00:43:37,260 --> 00:43:38,030
It's me.

613
00:43:38,700 --> 00:43:40,870
I'm Fangfei,
whom you have known since I was a kid.

614
00:43:46,580 --> 00:43:47,350
Li.

615
00:43:48,350 --> 00:43:49,510
It's you.

616
00:43:50,390 --> 00:43:52,070
You are still alive.

617
00:43:52,740 --> 00:43:53,430
Aunt.

618
00:43:55,350 --> 00:43:57,070
My father will be beheaded tomorrow.

619
00:43:58,300 --> 00:44:01,580
I would like you
to speak out in his defense.

620
00:44:05,870 --> 00:44:06,620
Close the door.

621
00:44:08,550 --> 00:44:09,220
Aunt.

622
00:44:11,910 --> 00:44:12,620
Aunt.

623
00:44:15,550 --> 00:44:16,180
Aunt.

624
00:44:17,910 --> 00:44:18,870
Please.

625
00:44:20,140 --> 00:44:20,950
I beg of you.

626
00:44:24,990 --> 00:44:25,910
Please.

627
00:44:26,620 --> 00:44:27,260
I beg of you.

628
00:44:27,470 --> 00:44:28,070
Li.

629
00:44:28,470 --> 00:44:28,870
Please.

630
00:44:29,030 --> 00:44:29,870
Good girl.

631
00:44:30,950 --> 00:44:32,780
Stand up. Don't kneel.

632
00:44:35,830 --> 00:44:36,550
Your hand...

633
00:44:38,470 --> 00:44:39,510
They did this.

634
00:44:40,830 --> 00:44:41,910
Did they do this to you?

635
00:44:44,950 --> 00:44:45,700
Come back!

636
00:44:57,510 --> 00:44:58,390
Uncle Liu's leg...

637
00:45:02,220 --> 00:45:07,660
Li, think of us as cowards.

638
00:45:07,910 --> 00:45:08,990
Just think of us

639
00:45:10,350 --> 00:45:11,660
as dead.

640
00:45:31,700 --> 00:45:33,030
Do good deeds

641
00:45:34,180 --> 00:45:36,180
really lead to good karma?

642
00:46:05,420 --> 00:46:10,900
♪If there are no happy memories♪

643
00:46:13,020 --> 00:46:18,500
♪How can we traverse
the forbidden land of sorrow?♪

644
00:46:20,300 --> 00:46:26,380
